15	 *
16	 * Middleware stack order (matters):
17	 *   1. requestId     — assigns ID before anything else so all logs include it
18	 *   2. logger        — logs request start/end with request ID
19	 *   3. metrics       — records latency / counts (wraps everything below)
20	 *   4. errorHandler  — catches all errors from router and downstream middleware
21	 *   5. bodyParser    — parses body after logging starts (body not logged at entry)
22	 *   6. auth          — session lookup; sets ctx.state.user
23	 *   7. router        — dispatches to module handlers
