326	   *   2. Concurrently call validateAndRotate — its FOR UPDATE NOWAIT will get PG error 55P03.
327	   *   3. The service waits 50 ms then retries.
328	   *   4. We release T1 after ~30 ms, so the retry (at ~50 ms) finds the row unlocked.
