19	 * Unauthenticated write requests (e.g. POST /v1/auth/login) are exempt.
20	 *
21	 * Atomicity guarantee: the slot is reserved via INSERT … ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
22	 * before the handler runs, so two concurrent requests with the same key race at the
23	 * DB level. Only one wins the INSERT; the other finds the existing record and either
24	 * replays the cached response or returns 409 (still pending).
25	 */
