2	/**
3	 * Promote scheduled entity versions whose effective_from date has arrived.
4	 *
5	 * Run daily (e.g., 00:05 UTC) via cron or a container restart policy:
6	 *   node scripts/promote-scheduled-versions.js
7	 *
8	 * For each entity type, finds all scheduled versions with effective_from <= today
9	 * and promotes the earliest-effective-date candidate to 'active', superseding the
10	 * current active version inside a single transaction per entity.
11	 *
12	 * Exit 0 on success, 1 on error.
